- cs.SI (Signal Processing): The paper introduces a new feature extractor based on signal processing techniques such as Gabor frames and Mallat's scattering transform. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the performance of the feature extractor on datasets and mentions the use of few training samples, indicating a machine learning aspect. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although the paper is focused on audio processing, the use of deep scattering networks and feature extraction techniques could also be relevant to computer vision and pattern recognition tasks. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper's focus on audio processing and feature extraction could also be relevant to multimedia applications.
